    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/462aab2edd670d86a4bc817954bdefc9.poster.avif?t=1759738062\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/462aab2edd670d86a4bc817954bdefc9.webm?t=1759738062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/462aab2edd670d86a4bc817954bdefc9.mp4?t=1759738062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/3ef2574cfcb58ac95c3bd461d5c93f69.avif?t=1759738062\" width=667 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The recent discovery of an archaeological site in southeastern Turkey has piqued the Vatican's interest. Elizabeth, a young member of the Pontifical Commission for Sacred Archaeology, has traveled to Sanliurfa to investigate the ruins of Göbekli Tepe. If the Commission is correct, the site could be concealing humanity's oldest site of worship... if this is the case, uncovering the its secrets could reveal the origins of all civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elizabeth must hurry, as she is well aware that the Vatican is not the only organization with its eyes on the hill of Göbekli Tepe, and the secrets hidden in the ancient sanctuary could be of great interest to numerous governments and intelligence agencies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elizabeth will quickly realize that she and the Commission are ill-prepared to grasp the true nature of the groundbreaking discovery...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/2f252aa8cefa7fa0762bdfe2a3034c8d.poster.avif?t=1759738062\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/2f252aa8cefa7fa0762bdfe2a3034c8d.webm?t=1759738062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/2f252aa8cefa7fa0762bdfe2a3034c8d.mp4?t=1759738062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/75130b7da26f29b5687ab5b3a98d35df.avif?t=1759738062\" width=667 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive thriller with elements of science fiction, adventure, and mystery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A point-and-click adventure game based on inventory puzzles, with a modern and intuitive interface.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed pixel-art environments based on real-world locations in Egypt, Turkey, and Vatican City during the 1970s.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cinematic close-ups, animations, and cutscenes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story influenced by the works of Peter LeMesurier, Zecharia Sitchin, and Erich von Däniken.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack by Michael Lückgen, inspired by the iconic scores of 'Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade' (John Williams) and 'Blade Runner' (Vangelis).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/88c0b6a57bb234f3f42507de82b4e80f.poster.avif?t=1759738062\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/88c0b6a57bb234f3f42507de82b4e80f.webm?t=1759738062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072050/extras/88c0b6a57bb234f3f42507de82b4e80f.mp4?t=1759738062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
